data.description: Welcome to your future! Nestled in the International District this immaculately taken care of home is ready for more love. The possibilities are near endless and so seems the backyard! Take advantage of plenty of space for a peaceful night under the stars, whether you're sitting on your front patio or under the gazebo. With tons of security & privacy this property will not last long! It's been loved so greatly you're sure to see it the moment you drive up! Enjoy newly updated venting hood, backsplash, lighting fixtures, bathroom vanity, water softener, water pressure regulator! Newer 3 y.o. roof! Newer 4 y.o. evaporative cooler! Updated flooring throughout! Only minutes from UNM, Downtown, Uptown, the Downs and so much more. Schedule your private tour today! Don't wait! Don't miss out
